#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:110
msgid ""
"Below these buttons is the Quick Field Calculation bar (enabled only in "
":ref:`edit mode <sec_edit_existing_layer>`), which allows to quickly apply "
"calculations to all or part of the features in the layer. This bar uses the "
"same :ref:`expressions <vector_expressions>` as the |calculateField| "
":sup:`Field Calculator` (see :ref:`calculate_fields_values`)."
msgstr ""
"Ispod ove dugmadi je traka za brzo računanje polja (omogućena samo u "
":ref:`režimu uređivanja <sec_edit_existing_layer>`), koja omogućava brzu "
"primenu izračunavanja na sve ili deo objekata u sloju. Ova traka koristi "
"iste :ref:`izraze <vector_expressions>` kao |calculateField| "
":sup:`Kalkulator polja` (pogledajte :ref:`calculate_fields_values`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:120
msgid "Table view vs Form view"
msgstr "Prikaz tabele naspram prikaza obrasca"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:122
msgid ""
"QGIS provides two view modes to easily manipulate data in the attribute "
"table:"
msgstr ""
"QGIS pruža dva režima prikaza za laku manipulaciju podacima u atributskoj "
"tabeli:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:124
msgid ""
"The |openTable| :sup:`Table view`, displays values of multiple features in a"
" tabular mode, each row representing a feature and each column a field. A "
"right-click on the column header allows you to :ref:`configure the table "
"display <configure_table_columns>` while a right-click on a cell provides "
":ref:`interaction with the feature <interacting_features_table>`."
msgstr ""
"|openTable| :sup:`Prikaz tabele` prikazuje vrednosti više objekata u "
"tabelarnom režimu, gde svaki red predstavlja objekat, a svaka kolona polje. "
"Desni klik na zaglavlje kolone omogućava vam da :ref:`konfigurišete prikaz "
"tabele <configure_table_columns>`, dok desni klik na ćeliju pruža "
":ref:`interakciju sa objektom <interacting_features_table>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:130
msgid ""
"The attribute table supports :kbd:`Shift+Mouse Wheel` scrolling in table "
"view mode to switch between vertical and horizontal scrolling movements. "
"This can also be achieved replacing the mouse with the trackpad on macOS."
msgstr ""
"Atributska tabela podržava skrolovanje pomoću :kbd:`Shift+Mouse Wheel` u "
"režimu prikaza tabele radi prebacivanja između vertikalnog i horizontalnog "
"kretanja skrolovanja. Ovo se takođe može postići zamenom miša trekpadom na "
"macOS-u."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:133
msgid ""
"The |formView| :sup:`Form view` shows :ref:`feature identifiers <maptips>` "
"in a first panel and displays only the attributes of the clicked identifier "
"in the second one. There is a pull-down menu at the top of the first panel "
"where the \"identifier\" can be updated using an attribute "
"(:menuselection:`Columns -->`) or an :guilabel:`Expression`. A "
":menuselection:`Sort... -->` menu allows you to sort the returned "
"identifiers :guilabel:`By display name (ascending)`, :guilabel:`By display "
"name (descending)` or :guilabel:`By custom expression`. The pull-down also "
"includes the last 10 expressions for reuse. Form view uses the layer fields "
"configuration (see :ref:`vector_attributes_menu`)."
msgstr ""
"|formView| :sup:`Prikaz obrasca` prikazuje :ref:`identifikatore objekata "
"<maptips>` u prvom panelu i prikazuje samo atribute objekta na koji je "
"kliknuto u drugom. Na vrhu prvog panela nalazi se padajući meni gde se "
"„identifikator“ može ažurirati pomoću atributa (:menuselection:`Kolone -->`)"
" ili :guilabel:`izraza`. Meni :menuselection:`Sortiraj... -->` omogućava vam"
" da sortirate vraćene identifikatore :guilabel:`Po prikazanom nazivu "
"(rastuće)`, :guilabel:`Po prikazanom nazivu (opadajuće)` ili :guilabel:`Po "
"prilagođenom izrazu`. Padajući meni takođe uključuje poslednjih 10 izraza za"
" ponovnu upotrebu. Prikaz obrasca koristi konfiguraciju polja sloja "
"(pogledajte :ref:`vector_attributes_menu`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:841
msgid "formView"
msgstr "formView"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:145
msgid ""
"You can browse through the feature identifiers with the arrows on the bottom"
" of the first panel. The features attributes update in the second panel as "
"you go. It's also possible to identify or move to the active feature in the "
"map canvas with pushing down any of the button at the bottom:"
msgstr ""
"Kroz identifikatore objekata možete se kretati pomoću strelica na dnu prvog "
"panela. Atributi objekata se ažuriraju u drugom panelu kako idete. Takođe je"
" moguće identifikovati ili preći na aktivni objekat na platnu karte "
"pritiskanjem bilo kog dugmeta na dnu:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:150
msgid ""
"|highlightFeature| :sup:`Highlight current feature` if visible in the map "
"canvas"
msgstr ""
"|highlightFeature| :sup:`Istakni trenutni objekat` ako je vidljiv na platnu "
"karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:847
msgid "highlightFeature"
msgstr "highlightFeature"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:152
msgid "|panTo| :sup:`Automatically pan to current feature`"
msgstr "|panTo| :sup:`Automatski pomeri na trenutni objekat`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:875
msgid "panTo"
msgstr "panTo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:153
msgid "|zoomTo| :sup:`Zoom to current feature`"
msgstr "|zoomTo| :sup:`Uveličaj na trenutni objekat`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:899
msgid "zoomTo"
msgstr "zoomTo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:155
msgid ""
"You can switch from one mode to the other by clicking the corresponding icon"
" at the bottom right of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Iz jednog režima u drugi možete se prebaciti klikom na odgovarajuću ikonu u "
"donjem desnom uglu dijaloga."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:158
msgid ""
"You can also specify the :guilabel:`Default view` mode at the opening of the"
" attribute table in :menuselection:`Settings --> Options --> Data Sources` "
"menu. It can be 'Remember last view', 'Table view' or 'Form view'."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete zadati režim :guilabel:`Podrazumevani prikaz` pri otvaranju "
"atributske tabele u meniju :menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije --> Izvori"
" podataka`. To može biti „Zapamti poslednji prikaz“, „Prikaz tabele“ ili "
"„Prikaz obrasca“."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:167
msgid "Attribute table in table view (top) vs form view (bottom)"
msgstr ""
"Atributska tabela u prikazu tabele (gore) naspram prikaza obrasca (dole)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:175
msgid "Configuring the columns"
msgstr "Konfigurisanje kolona"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:177
msgid ""
"Right-click in a column header when in table view to have access to tools "
"that help you control:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite desnim tasterom u zaglavlje kolone dok ste u prikazu tabele da "
"biste imali pristup alatkama koje vam pomažu da kontrolišete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:180
msgid "the :ref:`column(s) size <resize_columns>`"
msgstr ":ref:`veličinu kolone(a) <resize_columns>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:181
msgid "the :ref:`column(s) visibility and order <organize_columns>`"
msgstr ":ref:`vidljivost i redosled kolone(a) <organize_columns>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:182
msgid "the :ref:`sort order of the data <sort_columns>`"
msgstr ":ref:`redosled sortiranja podataka <sort_columns>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:187
msgid "Resizing columns widths"
msgstr "Promena širine kolona"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:189
msgid ""
"Columns width can be set through a right-click on the column header and "
"select either:"
msgstr ""
"Širina kolona može se postaviti desnim klikom na zaglavlje kolone i izborom "
"bilo:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Set width...` to enter the desired value. By default, the current"
" value is displayed in the widget"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Postavi širinu...` da biste uneli željenu vrednost. Podrazumevano"
" se u vidžetu prikazuje trenutna vrednost"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:194
msgid ":guilabel:`Set all column widths...` to the same value"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Postavi širine svih kolona...` na istu vrednost"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:195
msgid ":guilabel:`Autosize` to resize at the best fit the column."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Automatska veličina` za promenu veličine kolone na najbolje "
"uklapanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:196
msgid ":guilabel:`Autosize all columns`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Automatska veličina svih kolona`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:198
msgid ""
"A column size can also be changed by dragging the boundary on the right of "
"its heading. The new size of the column is maintained for the layer, and "
"restored at the next opening of the attribute table."
msgstr ""
"Veličina kolone se takođe može promeniti prevlačenjem granice sa desne "
"strane njenog zaglavlja. Nova veličina kolone se održava za sloj i vraća pri"
" sledećem otvaranju atributske tabele."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:202
msgid ""
"In the :ref:`Data Source Settings <datasources_options>`, you can choose to "
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Autosize all columns by default when opening attribute"
" table`, which will make \"Autosize All Columns\" the default view every "
"time attribute tables are opened in QGIS."
msgstr ""
"U :ref:`Podešavanjima izvora podataka <datasources_options>` možete izabrati"
" |checkbox| :guilabel:`Podrazumevano automatski postavi veličinu svih kolona"
" pri otvaranju atributske tabele`, čime će „Automatska veličina svih kolona“"
" postati podrazumevani prikaz svaki put kada se atributske tabele otvore u "
"QGIS-u."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:813
msgid "checkbox"
msgstr "checkbox"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:209
msgid "Hiding and organizing columns and enabling actions"
msgstr "Skrivanje i organizovanje kolona i omogućavanje radnji"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:211
msgid ""
"By right-clicking in a column header, you can choose to :guilabel:`Hide "
"column` from the attribute table (in \"table view\" mode). For more advanced"
" controls, press the |editTable| :sup:`Organize columns...` button from the "
"dialog toolbar or choose :guilabel:`Organize columns...` in a column header "
"contextual menu."
msgstr ""
"Desnim klikom u zaglavlje kolone možete izabrati :guilabel:`Sakrij kolonu` "
"iz atributske tabele (u režimu „prikaz tabele“). Za naprednije kontrole "
"pritisnite dugme |editTable| :sup:`Organizuj kolone...` iz palete alatki "
"dijaloga ili izaberite :guilabel:`Organizuj kolone...` u kontekstnom meniju "
"zaglavlja kolone."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:217
msgid "In the new dialog, you can:"
msgstr "U novom dijalogu možete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:219
msgid ""
"check/uncheck columns you want to show or hide: a hidden column will "
"disappear from every instance of the attribute table dialog until it is "
"actively restored. It is also possible to:"
msgstr ""
"označiti/odznačiti kolone koje želite da prikažete ili sakrijete: skrivena "
"kolona će nestati iz svake instance dijaloga atributske tabele dok se "
"aktivno ne vrati. Takođe je moguće:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:223
msgid ""
"choose :guilabel:`Show All` to display all the fields (columns) and actions "
"in the table"
msgstr ""
"izabrati :guilabel:`Prikaži sve` da biste prikazali sva polja (kolone) i "
"radnje u tabeli"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:224
msgid ""
"choose :guilabel:`Hide All` to hide all the fields (columns) and actions in "
"the table"
msgstr ""
"izabrati :guilabel:`Sakrij sve` da biste sakrili sva polja (kolone) i radnje"
" u tabeli"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:225
msgid ""
"use the :guilabel:`Toggle selection` to invert visibility of the current "
"selection of columns. You can use :ref:`keyboard combination "
"<interacting_features_table>` for selecting multiple columns."
msgstr ""
"koristiti :guilabel:`Preokreni izbor` da biste obrnuli vidljivost trenutnog "
"izbora kolona. Za izbor više kolona možete koristiti :ref:`kombinaciju "
"tastera <interacting_features_table>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:229
msgid ""
"drag-and-drop items to reorder the columns in the attribute table. Note that"
" this change is for the table rendering and does not alter the fields order "
"in the layer datasource"
msgstr ""
"prevući i ispustiti stavke radi preuređivanja kolona u atributskoj tabeli. "
"Imajte u vidu da je ova izmena za iscrtavanje tabele i ne menja redosled "
"polja u izvoru podataka sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:232
msgid ""
"add a new virtual :guilabel:`Actions` column that displays in each row a "
"drop-down box or a button list of enabled actions. See :ref:`actions_menu` "
"for more information about actions."
msgstr ""
"dodati novu virtuelnu kolonu :guilabel:`Radnje` koja u svakom redu prikazuje"
" padajući okvir ili listu dugmadi omogućenih radnji. Za više informacija o "
"radnjama pogledajte :ref:`actions_menu`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:240
msgid "Sorting rows"
msgstr "Sortiranje redova"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:242
msgid ""
"The rows can be sorted by any column, by clicking on the column header. A "
"small arrow indicates the sort order (downward pointing means descending "
"values from the top row down, upward pointing means ascending values from "
"the top row down). You can also choose to sort the rows with the "
":guilabel:`Sort...` option of the column header context menu and write an "
"expression. E.g. to sort the rows using multiple columns you can write "
"``concat(col0, col1)``."
msgstr ""
"Redovi se mogu sortirati po bilo kojoj koloni, klikom na zaglavlje kolone. "
"Mala strelica označava redosled sortiranja (strelica nadole znači opadajuće "
"vrednosti od gornjeg reda naniže, strelica nagore znači rastuće vrednosti od"
" gornjeg reda naniže). Takođe možete izabrati sortiranje redova pomoću "
"opcije :guilabel:`Sortiraj...` u kontekstnom meniju zaglavlja kolone i "
"napisati izraz. Npr. za sortiranje redova pomoću više kolona možete napisati"
" ``concat(col0, col1)``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:250
msgid ""
"In form view, features identifier can be sorted using the |sort| "
":guilabel:`Sort by preview expression` option."
msgstr ""
"U prikazu obrasca, identifikatori objekata mogu se sortirati pomoću opcije "
"|sort| :guilabel:`Sortiraj po izrazu pregleda`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:891
msgid "sort"
msgstr "sort"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:253
msgid ""
"Note that sorting the rows only affects the table rendering and does not "
"alter the features order in the layer datasource."
msgstr ""
"Imajte u vidu da sortiranje redova utiče samo na iscrtavanje tabele i ne "
"menja redosled objekata u izvoru podataka sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:258
msgid "**Sorting based on columns of different types**"
msgstr "**Sortiranje na osnovu kolona različitih tipova**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:260
msgid ""
"Trying to sort an attribute table based on columns of string and numeric "
"types may lead to unexpected result because of the ``concat(\"USE\", "
"\"ID\")`` expression returning string values (ie, ``'Borough105' < "
"'Borough6'``). You can workaround this by using eg ``concat(\"USE\", "
"lpad(\"ID\", 3, 0))`` which returns ``'Borough105' > 'Borough006'``."
msgstr ""
"Pokušaj sortiranja atributske tabele na osnovu kolona niskovnog i numeričkog"
" tipa može dovesti do neočekivanog rezultata jer izraz ``concat(\"USE\", "
"\"ID\")`` vraća niskovne vrednosti (tj. ``'Borough105' < 'Borough6'``). Ovo "
"možete zaobići korišćenjem npr. ``concat(\"USE\", lpad(\"ID\", 3, 0))`` koji"
" vraća ``'Borough105' > 'Borough006'``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:270
msgid "Formatting of table cells using conditions"
msgstr "Formatiranje ćelija tabele pomoću uslova"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:272
msgid ""
"Conditional formatting settings can be used to highlight in the attribute "
"table features you may want to put a particular focus on, using custom "
"conditions on feature's:"
msgstr ""
"Podešavanja uslovnog formatiranja mogu se koristiti za isticanje objekata u "
"atributskoj tabeli na koje biste možda želeli da stavite poseban fokus, "
"pomoću prilagođenih uslova na:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:276
msgid ""
"geometry (e.g., identifying multi-parts features, small area ones or in a "
"defined map extent...);"
msgstr ""
"geometriju objekta (npr. prepoznavanje višedelnih objekata, onih male "
"površine ili u definisanom obuhvatu karte...);"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:278
msgid ""
"or field value (e.g., comparing values to a threshold, identifying empty "
"cells, duplicates, ...)."
msgstr ""
"ili vrednost polja (npr. poređenje vrednosti sa pragom, prepoznavanje "
"praznih ćelija, duplikata, ...)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:281
msgid ""
"You can enable the conditional formatting panel clicking on "
"|conditionalFormatting| :sup:`Conditional formatting` button at the top "
"right of the attributes window in table view (not triggered in form view)."
msgstr ""
"Panel uslovnog formatiranja možete omogućiti klikom na dugme "
"|conditionalFormatting| :sup:`Uslovno formatiranje` u gornjem desnom uglu "
"prozora atributa u prikazu tabele (ne pokreće se u prikazu obrasca)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:285
msgid ""
"The new panel allows user to add new rules to format rendering of "
"|radioButtonOn|:guilabel:`Field` or |radioButtonOff|:guilabel:`Full row`. "
"Adding new rule opens a form to define:"
msgstr ""
"Novi panel omogućava korisniku da doda nova pravila za formatiranje "
"iscrtavanja |radioButtonOn|:guilabel:`Polja` ili "
"|radioButtonOff|:guilabel:`Celog reda`. Dodavanje novog pravila otvara "
"obrazac za definisanje:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:881
msgid "radioButtonOn"
msgstr "radioButtonOn"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:879
msgid "radioButtonOff"
msgstr "radioButtonOff"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:289
msgid "the name of the rule;"
msgstr "naziva pravila;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:290
msgid ""
"a condition using any of the :ref:`expression builder <vector_expressions>` "
"functions;"
msgstr ""
"uslova pomoću bilo koje funkcije :ref:`graditelja izraza "
"<vector_expressions>`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:291
msgid ""
"the formatting: it can be chosen from a list of predefined formats or "
"created based on properties like:"
msgstr ""
"formatiranja: može se izabrati iz liste unapred definisanih formata ili "
"napraviti na osnovu svojstava kao što su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:294
msgid "background and text colors;"
msgstr "boje pozadine i teksta;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:295
msgid "use of icon;"
msgstr "korišćenje ikone;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:296
msgid "bold, italic, underline, or strikeout;"
msgstr "podebljano, kurziv, podvučeno ili precrtano;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:297
msgid "font."
msgstr "font."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:304
msgid "Conditional Formatting of an attribute table"
msgstr "Uslovno formatiranje atributske tabele"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:311
msgid "Interacting with features in an attribute table"
msgstr "Interakcija sa objektima u atributskoj tabeli"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:314
msgid "Selecting features"
msgstr "Izbor objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:316
msgid ""
"In table view, each row in the attribute table displays the attributes of a "
"unique feature in the layer. Selecting a row selects the feature and "
"likewise, selecting a feature in the map canvas (in case of geometry enabled"
" layer) selects the row in the attribute table. If the set of features "
"selected in the map canvas (or attribute table) is changed, then the "
"selection is also updated in the attribute table (or map canvas) "
"accordingly."
msgstr ""
"U prikazu tabele, svaki red u atributskoj tabeli prikazuje atribute "
"jedinstvenog objekta u sloju. Izbor reda bira objekat, a isto tako, izbor "
"objekta na platnu karte (u slučaju sloja sa geometrijom) bira red u "
"atributskoj tabeli. Ako se skup objekata izabranih na platnu karte (ili "
"atributskoj tabeli) promeni, tada se izbor u skladu s tim ažurira i u "
"atributskoj tabeli (ili na platnu karte)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:323
msgid ""
"Rows can be selected by clicking on the row number on the left side of the "
"row. **Multiple rows** can be marked by holding the :kbd:`Ctrl` key. A "
"**continuous selection** can be made by holding the :kbd:`Shift` key and "
"clicking on several row headers on the left side of the rows. All rows "
"between the current cursor position and the clicked row are selected. Moving"
" the cursor position in the attribute table, by clicking a cell in the "
"table, does not change the row selection. Changing the selection in the main"
" canvas does not move the cursor position in the attribute table."
msgstr ""
"Redovi se mogu izabrati klikom na broj reda sa leve strane reda. **Više "
"redova** može se označiti držanjem tastera :kbd:`Ctrl`. **Neprekidan izbor**"
" može se napraviti držanjem tastera :kbd:`Shift` i klikom na nekoliko "
"zaglavlja redova sa leve strane redova. Svi redovi između trenutnog položaja"
" pokazivača i reda na koji je kliknuto biće izabrani. Pomeranje položaja "
"pokazivača u atributskoj tabeli, klikom na ćeliju u tabeli, ne menja izbor "
"reda. Promena izbora na glavnom platnu ne pomera položaj pokazivača u "
"atributskoj tabeli."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:332
msgid ""
"In form view of the attribute table, features are by default identified in "
"the left panel by the value of their displayed field (see :ref:`maptips`). "
"This identifier can be replaced using the drop-down list at the top of the "
"panel, either by selecting an existing field or using a custom expression. "
"You can also choose to sort the list of features from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"U prikazu obrasca atributske tabele, objekti se podrazumevano identifikuju u"
" levom panelu vrednošću svog prikazanog polja (pogledajte :ref:`maptips`). "
"Ovaj identifikator se može zameniti pomoću padajuće liste na vrhu panela, "
"bilo izborom postojećeg polja ili korišćenjem prilagođenog izraza. Takođe "
"možete izabrati sortiranje liste objekata iz padajućeg menija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:338
msgid ""
"Click a value in the left panel to display the feature's attributes in the "
"right one. To select a feature, you need to click inside the square symbol "
"at the left of the identifier. By default, the symbol turns into yellow. "
"Like in the table view, you can perform multiple feature selection using the"
" keyboard combinations previously exposed."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na vrednost u levom panelu da biste prikazali atribute objekta u "
"desnom. Da biste izabrali objekat, potrebno je da kliknete unutar kvadratnog"
" simbola sa leve strane identifikatora. Podrazumevano simbol postaje žut. "
"Kao u prikazu tabele, možete izabrati više objekata pomoću prethodno "
"izloženih kombinacija tastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:347
msgid ""
"Beyond selecting features with the mouse, you can perform automatic "
"selection based on feature's attribute using tools available in the "
"attribute table toolbar, such as (see section :ref:`automatic_selection` and"
" subsequent for more information and use case):"
msgstr ""
"Osim izbora objekata mišem, možete izvršiti automatski izbor na osnovu "
"atributa objekta pomoću alatki dostupnih u paleti alatki atributske tabele, "
"kao što su (za više informacija i primere upotrebe pogledajte odeljak "
":ref:`automatic_selection` i naredne):"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:352
msgid "|expressionSelect| :guilabel:`Select By Expression...`"
msgstr "|expressionSelect| :guilabel:`Izaberi pomoću izraza...`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:353
msgid "|formSelect| :guilabel:`Select Features By Value...`"
msgstr "|formSelect| :guilabel:`Izaberi objekte po vrednosti...`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:354
msgid "|deselectActiveLayer| :guilabel:`Deselect All Features from the Layer`"
msgstr ""
"|deselectActiveLayer| :guilabel:`Poništi izbor svih objekata iz sloja`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:355
msgid "|selectAll| :guilabel:`Select All Features`"
msgstr "|selectAll| :guilabel:`Izaberi sve objekte`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:356
msgid "|invertSelection| :guilabel:`Invert Feature Selection`."
msgstr "|invertSelection| :guilabel:`Obrni izbor objekata`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:358
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`select features using forms "
"<filter_select_form>`."
msgstr ""
"Takođe je moguće :ref:`izabrati objekte pomoću obrazaca "
"<filter_select_form>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:364
msgid "Filtering features"
msgstr "Filtriranje objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:366
msgid ""
"Once you have selected features in the attribute table, you may want to "
"display only these records in the table. This can be easily done using the "
":guilabel:`Show Selected Features` item from the drop-down list at the "
"bottom left of the attribute table dialog. This list offers the following "
"filters:"
msgstr ""
"Kada izaberete objekte u atributskoj tabeli, možda ćete želeti da prikažete "
"samo te zapise u tabeli. To se lako radi pomoću stavke :guilabel:`Prikaži "
"izabrane objekte` iz padajuće liste u donjem levom uglu dijaloga atributske "
"tabele. Ova lista nudi sledeće filtere:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:371
msgid "|openTable| :guilabel:`Show All Features`"
msgstr "|openTable| :guilabel:`Prikaži sve objekte`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:372
msgid ""
"|openTableSelected| :guilabel:`Show Selected Features` - same as using "
":guilabel:`Open Attribute Table (Selected Features)` from the "
":guilabel:`Layer` menu or the :guilabel:`Attributes Toolbar` or pressing "
":kbd:`Shift+F6`"
msgstr ""
"|openTableSelected| :guilabel:`Prikaži izabrane objekte` - isto kao "
"korišćenje :guilabel:`Otvori atributsku tabelu (izabrani objekti)` iz menija"
" :guilabel:`Sloj` ili :guilabel:`palete alatki Atributi` ili pritiskanje "
":kbd:`Shift+F6`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:871
msgid "openTableSelected"
msgstr "openTableSelected"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:375
msgid ""
"|openTableVisible| :guilabel:`Show Features visible on map` - same as using "
":guilabel:`Open Attribute Table (Visible Features)` from the "
":guilabel:`Layer` menu or the :guilabel:`Attributes Toolbar` or pressing "
":kbd:`Ctrl+F6`"
msgstr ""
"|openTableVisible| :guilabel:`Prikaži objekte vidljive na karti` - isto kao "
"korišćenje :guilabel:`Otvori atributsku tabelu (vidljivi objekti)` iz menija"
" :guilabel:`Sloj` ili :guilabel:`palete alatki Atributi` ili pritiskanje "
":kbd:`Ctrl+F6`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:873
msgid "openTableVisible"
msgstr "openTableVisible"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:378
msgid ""
"|openTableInvalid| :guilabel:`Show Features with Failing Constraints` - "
"features will be filtered to only show the ones which have failing "
":ref:`constraints <constraints>`. Depending on whether the unmet constraint "
"is hard or soft, failing field values are displayed in respectively dark or "
"light orange cells."
msgstr ""
"|openTableInvalid| :guilabel:`Prikaži objekte sa neispunjenim ograničenjima`"
" - objekti će biti filtrirani da prikažu samo one koji imaju neispunjena "
":ref:`ograničenja <constraints>`. U zavisnosti od toga da li je neispunjeno "
"ograničenje tvrdo ili meko, neispravne vrednosti polja prikazuju se redom u "
"tamno ili svetlo narandžastim ćelijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:869
msgid "openTableInvalid"
msgstr "openTableInvalid"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:382
msgid ""
"|openTableEdited| :guilabel:`Show Edited and New Features` - same as using "
":guilabel:`Open Attribute Table (Edited and New Features)` from the "
":guilabel:`Layer` menu or the :guilabel:`Attributes Toolbar`"
msgstr ""
"|openTableEdited| :guilabel:`Prikaži uređene i nove objekte` - isto kao "
"korišćenje :guilabel:`Otvori atributsku tabelu (uređeni i novi objekti)` iz "
"menija :guilabel:`Sloj` ili :guilabel:`palete alatki Atributi`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:867
msgid "openTableEdited"
msgstr "openTableEdited"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:385
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Field Filter` - allows the user to filter based on value of a "
"field: choose a column from a list, type or select a value and press "
":kbd:`Enter` to filter. Then, only the features matching ``num_field = "
"value`` or ``string_field ilike '%value%'`` expression are shown in the "
"attribute table. You can check |checkbox| :guilabel:`Case sensitive` to be "
"less permissive with strings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Filter polja` - omogućava korisniku da filtrira na osnovu "
"vrednosti polja: izaberite kolonu iz liste, unesite ili izaberite vrednost i"
" pritisnite :kbd:`Enter` za filtriranje. Zatim se u atributskoj tabeli "
"prikazuju samo objekti koji odgovaraju izrazu ``num_field = value`` ili "
"``string_field ilike '%value%'``. Možete označiti |checkbox| "
":guilabel:`Osetljivo na velika/mala slova` da biste bili manje popustljivi "
"sa niskama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:390
msgid ""
"|filterMap| :guilabel:`Advanced filter (Expression)` - Opens the expression "
"builder dialog. Within it, you can create :ref:`complex expressions "
"<vector_expressions>` to match table rows. For example, you can filter the "
"table using more than one field. When applied, the filter expression will "
"show up at the bottom of the form."
msgstr ""
"|filterMap| :guilabel:`Napredni filter (izraz)` - Otvara dijalog graditelja "
"izraza. Unutar njega možete praviti :ref:`složene izraze "
"<vector_expressions>` za podudaranje redova tabele. Na primer, možete "
"filtrirati tabelu pomoću više od jednog polja. Kada se primeni, izraz "
"filtera će se pojaviti na dnu obrasca."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:395
msgid ""
"|handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked| :menuselection:`Stored filter "
"expressions -->`: a shortcut to :ref:`saved expressions <store_filter>` "
"frequently used for filtering your attribute table."
msgstr ""
"|handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked| :menuselection:`Sačuvani izrazi filtera"
" -->`: prečica do :ref:`sačuvanih izraza <store_filter>` koji se često "
"koriste za filtriranje vaše atributske tabele."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:843
msgid "handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked"
msgstr "handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:398
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`filter features using forms "
"<filter_select_form>`."
msgstr ""
"Takođe je moguće :ref:`filtrirati objekte pomoću obrazaca "
"<filter_select_form>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:402
msgid ""
"Filtering records out of the attribute table does not filter features out of"
" the layer; they are simply momentaneously hidden from the table and can be "
"accessed from the map canvas or by removing the filter. For filters that do "
"hide features from the layer, use the :ref:`Query Builder "
"<vector_query_builder>`."
msgstr ""
"Filtriranje zapisa iz atributske tabele ne filtrira objekte iz sloja; oni su"
" samo trenutno sakriveni iz tabele i mogu se pristupiti sa platna karte ili "
"uklanjanjem filtera. Za filtere koji sakrivaju objekte iz sloja koristite "
":ref:`Graditelj upita <vector_query_builder>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:408
msgid "**Update datasource filtering with** ``Show Features Visible on Map``"
msgstr ""
"**Ažuriraj filtriranje izvora podataka pomoću** ``Prikaži objekte vidljive "
"na karti``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:410
msgid ""
"When for performance reasons, features shown in attribute table are "
"spatially limited to the canvas extent at its opening (see :ref:`Data Source"
" Options <tip_table_filtering>` for a how-to), selecting :guilabel:`Show "
"Features Visible on Map` on a new canvas extent updates the spatial "
"restriction."
msgstr ""
"Kada su, iz razloga performansi, objekti prikazani u atributskoj tabeli "
"prostorno ograničeni na obuhvat platna pri njenom otvaranju (za uputstvo "
"pogledajte :ref:`Opcije izvora podataka <tip_table_filtering>`), izbor "
":guilabel:`Prikaži objekte vidljive na karti` na novom obuhvatu platna "
"ažurira prostorno ograničenje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:419
msgid "Storing filter expressions"
msgstr "Čuvanje izraza filtera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:421
msgid ""
"Expressions you use for attribute table filtering can be saved for further "
"calls. When using :guilabel:`Field Filter` or :guilabel:`Advanced Filter "
"(expression)` entries, the expression used is displayed in a text widget in "
"the bottom of the attribute table dialog. Press the "
"|handleStoreFilterExpressionUnchecked| :sup:`Save expression with text as "
"name` next to the box to save the expression in the project. Pressing the "
"drop-down menu next to the button allows to save the expression with a "
"custom name (:guilabel:`Save expression as...`). Once a saved expression is "
"displayed, the |handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked| button is triggered and "
"its drop-down menu allows you to :guilabel:`Edit the expression` and name if"
" any, or :guilabel:`Delete stored expression`."
msgstr ""
"Izrazi koje koristite za filtriranje atributske tabele mogu se sačuvati za "
"naredne pozive. Pri korišćenju stavki :guilabel:`Filter polja` ili "
":guilabel:`Napredni filter (izraz)`, korišćeni izraz se prikazuje u "
"tekstualnom vidžetu na dnu dijaloga atributske tabele. Pritisnite "
"|handleStoreFilterExpressionUnchecked| :sup:`Sačuvaj izraz sa tekstom kao "
"nazivom` pored okvira da biste sačuvali izraz u projektu. Pritiskanje "
"padajućeg menija pored dugmeta omogućava čuvanje izraza sa prilagođenim "
"nazivom (:guilabel:`Sačuvaj izraz kao...`). Kada se sačuvani izraz prikaže, "
"aktivira se dugme |handleStoreFilterExpressionChecked|, a njegov padajući "
"meni omogućava vam da :guilabel:`Uredite izraz` i naziv ako postoji, ili "
":guilabel:`Obrišete sačuvani izraz`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:845
msgid "handleStoreFilterExpressionUnchecked"
msgstr "handleStoreFilterExpressionUnchecked"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:432
msgid ""
"Saved filter expressions are saved in the project and available through the "
":guilabel:`Stored filter expressions` menu of the attribute table. They are "
"different from the :ref:`user expressions <user_expressions_functions>`, "
"shared by all projects of the active user profile."
msgstr ""
"Sačuvani izrazi filtera čuvaju se u projektu i dostupni su preko menija "
":guilabel:`Sačuvani izrazi filtera` atributske tabele. Razlikuju se od "
":ref:`korisničkih izraza <user_expressions_functions>`, koje dele svi "
"projekti aktivnog korisničkog profila."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:440
msgid "Filtering and selecting features using forms"
msgstr "Filtriranje i izbor objekata pomoću obrazaca"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:442
msgid ""
"Clicking the |filterMap| :sup:`Filter/Select features using form` or "
"pressing :kbd:`Ctrl+F` will make the attribute table dialog switch to form "
"view and replace each widget with its search variant."
msgstr ""
"Klik na |filterMap| :sup:`Filtriraj/izaberi objekte pomoću obrasca` ili "
"pritiskanje :kbd:`Ctrl+F` će prebaciti dijalog atributske tabele u prikaz "
"obrasca i zameniti svaki vidžet njegovom varijantom za pretragu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:446
msgid ""
"From this point onwards, this tool functionality is similar to the one "
"described in :ref:`select_by_value`, where you can find descriptions of all "
"operators and selecting modes."
msgstr ""
"Od ove tačke nadalje, funkcionalnost ovog alata slična je onoj opisanoj u "
":ref:`select_by_value`, gde možete pronaći opise svih operatora i režima "
"izbora."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:455
msgid "Attribute table filtered by the filter form"
msgstr "Atributska tabela filtrirana obrascem za filtriranje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:457
msgid ""
"When selecting / filtering features from the attribute table, there is a "
":guilabel:`Filter features` button that allows defining and refining "
"filters. Its use triggers the :guilabel:`Advanced filter (Expression)` "
"option and displays the corresponding filter expression in an editable text "
"widget at the bottom of the form."
msgstr ""
"Pri izboru / filtriranju objekata iz atributske tabele, postoji dugme "
":guilabel:`Filtriraj objekte` koje omogućava definisanje i preciziranje "
"filtera. Njegovo korišćenje pokreće opciju :guilabel:`Napredni filter "
"(izraz)` i prikazuje odgovarajući izraz filtera u tekstualnom vidžetu koji "
"se može uređivati na dnu obrasca."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:462
msgid ""
"If there are already filtered features, you can refine the filter using the "
"drop-down list next to the :guilabel:`Filter features` button. The options "
"are:"
msgstr ""
"Ako već postoje filtrirani objekti, filter možete precizirati pomoću "
"padajuće liste pored dugmeta :guilabel:`Filtriraj objekte`. Opcije su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:465
msgid ":guilabel:`Filter within (\"AND\")`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Filtriraj unutar („AND“)`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:466
msgid ":guilabel:`Extend filter (\"OR\")`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Proširi filter („OR“)`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:468
msgid ""
"To clear the filter, either select the :guilabel:`Show all features` option "
"from the bottom left pull-down menu, or clear the expression and click "
":guilabel:`Apply` or press :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Da biste očistili filter, ili izaberite opciju :guilabel:`Prikaži sve "
"objekte` iz padajućeg menija u donjem levom uglu, ili očistite izraz i "
"kliknite na :guilabel:`Primeni` ili pritisnite :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:473
msgid "More actions on features"
msgstr "Više radnji nad objektima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:475
msgid ""
"Users have several possibilities to manipulate feature in an attribute "
"table. Right-click in a cell and you can:"
msgstr ""
"Korisnici imaju nekoliko mogućnosti za manipulaciju objektom u atributskoj "
"tabeli. Kliknite desnim tasterom u ćeliju i možete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:478
msgid ":guilabel:`Select all` (:kbd:`Ctrl+A`) the features;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Izabrati sve` (:kbd:`Ctrl+A`) objekte;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:479
msgid ""
"Copy the content of a cell in the clipboard with :guilabel:`Copy cell "
"content`;"
msgstr ""
"Kopirati sadržaj ćelije u ostavu pomoću :guilabel:`Kopiraj sadržaj ćelije`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:480
msgid ":guilabel:`Zoom to feature` without having to select it beforehand;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uveličati na objekat` bez potrebe da ga prethodno izaberete;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:481
msgid ":guilabel:`Pan to feature` without having to select it beforehand;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pomeriti na objekat` bez potrebe da ga prethodno izaberete;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:482
msgid ":guilabel:`Flash feature`, to highlight it in the map canvas;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bljesni objekat`, da biste ga istakli na platnu karte;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:483
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Open form`: it toggles attribute table into form view with a "
"focus on the clicked feature."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Otvori obrazac`: prebacuje atributsku tabelu u prikaz obrasca sa "
"fokusom na objekat na koji je kliknuto."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:485
msgid ""
"Display a :ref:`list of actions <actions_menu>`, previously enabled in the "
":menuselection:`Layer properties --> Actions` tab."
msgstr ""
"Prikazati :ref:`listu radnji <actions_menu>`, prethodno omogućenih u kartici"
" :menuselection:`Svojstva sloja --> Radnje`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:493
msgid "Copy cell content button"
msgstr "Dugme Kopiraj sadržaj ćelije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:497
msgid ""
"If you want to use attribute data in external programs (such as Excel, "
"LibreOffice, or a custom web application), select one or more row(s) and use"
" the |copySelected| :sup:`Copy selected rows to clipboard` button or press "
":kbd:`Ctrl+C`. Moreover, in :menuselection:`Settings --> Options --> Data "
"Sources` menu you can define the format to paste to with the :guilabel:`Copy"
" features as` option. More details at :ref:`datasources_options`."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da koristite atributske podatke u spoljnim programima (kao što su"
" Excel, LibreOffice ili prilagođena veb aplikacija), izaberite jedan ili "
"više redova i koristite dugme |copySelected| :sup:`Kopiraj izabrane redove u"
" ostavu` ili pritisnite :kbd:`Ctrl+C`. Osim toga, u meniju "
":menuselection:`Podešavanja --> Opcije --> Izvori podataka` možete "
"definisati format u koji se lepi pomoću opcije :guilabel:`Kopiraj objekte "
"kao`. Više detalja na :ref:`datasources_options`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:510
msgid "Editing attribute values"
msgstr "Uređivanje vrednosti atributa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:512
msgid ""
"In order to modify data in an attribute table, you should first toggle the "
"layer into edit. Press the |toggleEditing| :sup:`Toggle Editing` button. "
"Depending on the layer geometry type and the clipboard state, a few more "
"tools are enabled in the attribute table top toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Da biste izmenili podatke u atributskoj tabeli, prvo treba da prebacite sloj"
" u režim uređivanja. Pritisnite dugme |toggleEditing| :sup:`Uključi/isključi"
" uređivanje`. U zavisnosti od tipa geometrije sloja i stanja ostave, još "
"nekoliko alatki se omogućava u gornjoj paleti alatki atributske tabele."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:517
msgid "Editing attribute values can then be done by:"
msgstr "Uređivanje vrednosti atributa se zatim može obaviti:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:519
msgid ""
"typing the new value directly in the cell, whether the attribute table is in"
" table or form view. Changes are hence done cell by cell, feature by "
"feature;"
msgstr ""
"kucanjem nove vrednosti direktno u ćeliju, bilo da je atributska tabela u "
"prikazu tabele ili obrasca. Izmene se dakle vrše ćeliju po ćeliju, objekat "
"po objekat;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:521
msgid ""
"using the :ref:`field calculator <vector_field_calculator>`: update in a row"
" a field that may already exist or to be created but for multiple features. "
"It can be used to create virtual fields;"
msgstr ""
"korišćenjem :ref:`kalkulatora polja <vector_field_calculator>`: ažuriranje "
"odjednom polja koje možda već postoji ili tek treba da bude napravljeno, ali"
" za više objekata. Može se koristiti za pravljenje virtuelnih polja;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:524
msgid ""
"using the quick field :ref:`calculation bar <quick_field_calculation_bar>`: "
"same as above but for only existing field;"
msgstr ""
"korišćenjem trake za brzo :ref:`računanje polja "
"<quick_field_calculation_bar>`: isto kao gore, ali samo za postojeće polje;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:526
msgid ""
"or using the :ref:`multi edit <multi_edit_fields>` mode: update in a row "
"multiple fields for multiple features."
msgstr ""
"ili korišćenjem režima :ref:`višestrukog uređivanja <multi_edit_fields>`: "
"ažuriranje odjednom više polja za više objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:529
msgid ""
"Putting the layer into edit mode will also allow you to |editPaste| "
":sup:`Paste features from clipboard` (:kbd:`Ctrl+V`) |editCut| :sup:`Cut "
"selected rows to clipboard` (:kbd:`Ctrl+X`) or |deleteSelectedFeatures| "
":sup:`Delete selected features`. More details at :ref:`clipboard_feature`."
msgstr ""
"Prebacivanje sloja u režim uređivanja takođe će vam omogućiti da |editPaste|"
" :sup:`Nalepite objekte iz ostave` (:kbd:`Ctrl+V`), |editCut| :sup:`Isečete "
"izabrane redove u ostavu` (:kbd:`Ctrl+X`) ili |deleteSelectedFeatures| "
":sup:`Obrišete izabrane objekte`. Više detalja na :ref:`clipboard_feature`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:538
msgid "Using the Field Calculator"
msgstr "Korišćenje kalkulatora polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:540
msgid ""
"The |calculateField| :sup:`Field Calculator` button in the attribute table "
"allows you to perform calculations on the basis of existing attribute values"
" or defined functions, for instance, to calculate length or area of geometry"
" features. The results can be used to update an existing field, or written "
"to a new field (that can be a :ref:`virtual <virtual_field>` one)."
msgstr ""
"Dugme |calculateField| :sup:`Kalkulator polja` u atributskoj tabeli "
"omogućava vam da vršite izračunavanja na osnovu postojećih vrednosti "
"atributa ili definisanih funkcija, na primer, za računanje dužine ili "
"površine geometrijskih objekata. Rezultati se mogu koristiti za ažuriranje "
"postojećeg polja ili upisati u novo polje (koje može biti :ref:`virtuelno "
"<virtual_field>`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:546
msgid ""
"The field calculator is available on any layer that supports edit. When you "
"click on the field calculator icon the dialog opens (see "
":numref:`figure_field_calculator`). If the layer is not in edit mode, a "
"warning is displayed and using the field calculator will cause the layer to "
"be put in edit mode before the calculation is made."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator polja dostupan je na bilo kom sloju koji podržava uređivanje. "
"Kada kliknete na ikonu kalkulatora polja, otvara se dijalog (pogledajte "
":numref:`figure_field_calculator`). Ako sloj nije u režimu uređivanja, "
"prikazuje se upozorenje, a korišćenje kalkulatora polja uzrokovaće da sloj "
"bude prebačen u režim uređivanja pre nego što se izvrši izračunavanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:552
msgid ""
"Based on the :ref:`Expression Builder <expression_builder>` dialog, the "
"field calculator dialog offers a complete interface to define an expression "
"and apply it to an existing or a newly created field. To use the field "
"calculator dialog, you must select whether you want to:"
msgstr ""
"Zasnovan na dijalogu :ref:`Graditelj izraza <expression_builder>`, dijalog "
"kalkulatora polja nudi kompletan interfejs za definisanje izraza i njegovu "
"primenu na postojeće ili novonapravljeno polje. Da biste koristili dijalog "
"kalkulatora polja, morate izabrati da li želite da:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:557
msgid "apply calculation on the whole layer or on selected features only"
msgstr "primenite izračunavanje na ceo sloj ili samo na izabrane objekte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:558
msgid "create a new field for the calculation or update an existing one."
msgstr "napravite novo polje za izračunavanje ili ažurirate postojeće."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:565
msgid "Field Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:567
msgid ""
"If you choose to add a new field, you need to enter a field name, a field "
"type (integer, real, date or string) and if needed, the total field length "
"and the field precision. For example, if you choose a field length of 10 and"
" a field precision of 3, it means you have 7 digits before the dot, and 3 "
"digits for the decimal part."
msgstr ""
"Ako izaberete da dodate novo polje, potrebno je da unesete naziv polja, tip "
"polja (ceo broj, realni, datum ili niska) i, ako je potrebno, ukupnu dužinu "
"polja i preciznost polja. Na primer, ako izaberete dužinu polja 10 i "
"preciznost polja 3, to znači da imate 7 cifara pre tačke i 3 cifre za "
"decimalni deo."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:573
msgid ""
"A short example illustrates how field calculator works when using the "
":guilabel:`Expression` tab. We want to calculate the length in km of the "
"``railroads`` layer from the QGIS sample dataset:"
msgstr ""
"Kratak primer ilustruje kako kalkulator polja radi pri korišćenju kartice "
":guilabel:`Izraz`. Želimo da izračunamo dužinu u km sloja ``railroads`` iz "
"QGIS uzornog skupa podataka:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:577
msgid ""
"Load the shapefile :file:`railroads.shp` in QGIS and press |openTable| "
":sup:`Open Attribute Table`."
msgstr ""
"Učitajte shapefile :file:`railroads.shp` u QGIS i pritisnite |openTable| "
":sup:`Otvori atributsku tabelu`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:579
msgid ""
"Click on |toggleEditing| :sup:`Toggle editing mode` and open the "
"|calculateField| :sup:`Field Calculator` dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na |toggleEditing| :sup:`Uključi/isključi režim uređivanja` i "
"otvorite dijalog |calculateField| :sup:`Kalkulator polja`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:581
msgid ""
"Select the |checkbox| :guilabel:`Create a new field` checkbox to save the "
"calculations into a new field."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite polje za potvrdu |checkbox| :guilabel:`Napravi novo polje` da "
"biste sačuvali izračunavanja u novo polje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:583
msgid "Set :guilabel:`Output field name` to  ``length_km``"
msgstr "Postavite :guilabel:`Naziv izlaznog polja` na ``length_km``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:584
msgid "Select ``Decimal number (real)`` as :guilabel:`Output field type`"
msgstr ""
"Izaberite ``Decimalni broj (realni)`` kao :guilabel:`Tip izlaznog polja`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:585
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Output field length` to ``10`` and the "
":guilabel:`Precision` to ``3``"
msgstr ""
"Postavite :guilabel:`Dužinu izlaznog polja` na ``10`` i "
":guilabel:`Preciznost` na ``3``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:586
msgid ""
"Double click on ``$length`` in the :guilabel:`Geometry` group to add the "
"length of the geometry into the Field calculator expression box (you will "
"begin to see a preview of the output, up to 60 characters, below the "
"expression box updating in real-time as the expression is assembled)."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite na ``$length`` u grupi :guilabel:`Geometrija` da biste dodali "
"dužinu geometrije u okvir izraza kalkulatora polja (počećete da vidite "
"pregled izlaza, do 60 znakova, ispod okvira izraza koji se ažurira u realnom"
" vremenu kako se izraz sastavlja)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:590
msgid ""
"Complete the expression by typing ``/ 1000`` in the Field calculator "
"expression box and click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"Dovršite izraz kucanjem ``/ 1000`` u okvir izraza kalkulatora polja i "
"kliknite na :guilabel:`OK`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:592
msgid ""
"You can now find a new :guilabel:`length_km` field in the attribute table."
msgstr ""
"Sada u atributskoj tabeli možete pronaći novo polje :guilabel:`length_km`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:597
msgid "Creating a Virtual Field"
msgstr "Pravljenje virtuelnog polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:599
msgid ""
"A virtual field is a field based on an expression calculated on the fly, "
"meaning that its value is automatically updated as soon as an underlying "
"parameter changes. The expression applies to all the features in the layer "
"and is set once; you no longer need to recalculate the field each time "
"underlying values change. For example, you may want to use a virtual field "
"if you need area to be evaluated as you digitize features or to "
"automatically calculate a duration between dates that may change (e.g., "
"using ``now()`` function)."
msgstr ""
"Virtuelno polje je polje zasnovano na izrazu koji se izračunava u hodu, što "
"znači da se njegova vrednost automatski ažurira čim se promeni neki od "
"parametara koji stoje u osnovi. Izraz se primenjuje na sve objekte u sloju i"
" postavlja se jednom; više ne morate ponovo računati polje svaki put kada se"
" osnovne vrednosti promene. Na primer, možda ćete želeti da koristite "
"virtuelno polje ako je potrebno da se površina izračunava dok digitalizujete"
" objekte ili da se automatski računa trajanje između datuma koji se mogu "
"promeniti (npr. pomoću funkcije ``now()``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:607
msgid ""
"Creating a virtual field is done through the |calculateField| "
":guilabel:`Field calculator` dialog and follows the :ref:`same procedure "
"<vector_field_calculator>` as for regular fields. Simply remember to check "
"the |checkbox| :guilabel:`Create virtual field` option and use a field type "
"compatible with the data your expression would generate."
msgstr ""
"Pravljenje virtuelnog polja obavlja se kroz dijalog |calculateField| "
":guilabel:`Kalkulator polja` i prati :ref:`isti postupak "
"<vector_field_calculator>` kao za obična polja. Samo zapamtite da označite "
"opciju |checkbox| :guilabel:`Napravi virtuelno polje` i koristite tip polja "
"kompatibilan sa podacima koje bi vaš izraz generisao."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:612
msgid ""
"Editing a virtual field is done through the |sourceFields| "
":guilabel:`Fields` tab of the layer properties dialog (see "
":ref:`vector_fields_menu`). The expression defining the field is exposed in "
"the :guilabel:`Comment` column, and pressing the |expression| button next to"
" it opens an expression editor window for update."
msgstr ""
"Uređivanje virtuelnog polja obavlja se kroz karticu |sourceFields| "
":guilabel:`Polja` dijaloga svojstava sloja (pogledajte "
":ref:`vector_fields_menu`). Izraz koji definiše polje prikazan je u koloni "
":guilabel:`Komentar`, a pritiskanje dugmeta |expression| pored njega otvara "
"prozor uređivača izraza za ažuriranje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:893
msgid "sourceFields"
msgstr "sourceFields"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:833
msgid "expression"
msgstr "expression"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:618
msgid "**Use of Virtual Fields**"
msgstr "**Korišćenje virtuelnih polja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:620
msgid "A field can be set virtual only at its creation."
msgstr "Polje se može postaviti kao virtuelno samo pri njegovom pravljenju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:621
msgid ""
"Virtual fields are not permanent in the layer attributes, meaning that "
"they're only saved and available in the project file they've been created."
msgstr ""
"Virtuelna polja nisu trajna u atributima sloja, što znači da se čuvaju i "
"dostupna su samo u datoteci projekta u kojoj su napravljena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:628
msgid "Using the Quick Field Calculation Bar"
msgstr "Korišćenje trake za brzo računanje polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:630
msgid ""
"While Field calculator is always available, the quick field calculation bar "
"on top of the attribute table is only visible if the layer is in edit mode. "
"Thanks to the expression engine, it offers a quicker access to edit an "
"already existing field:"
msgstr ""
"Dok je kalkulator polja uvek dostupan, traka za brzo računanje polja na vrhu"
" atributske tabele vidljiva je samo ako je sloj u režimu uređivanja. "
"Zahvaljujući mehanizmu za izraze, ona nudi brži pristup uređivanju već "
"postojećeg polja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:635
msgid "Select the field to update in the drop-down list."
msgstr "Izaberite polje za ažuriranje u padajućoj listi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:636
msgid ""
"Fill the textbox with a value, an expression you directly write or build "
"using the |expression| expression button."
msgstr ""
"Popunite tekstualni okvir vrednošću, izrazom koji direktno napišete ili "
"napravite pomoću dugmeta izraza |expression|."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:638
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Update All`, :guilabel:`Update Selected` or "
":guilabel:`Update Filtered` button according to your need."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na dugme :guilabel:`Ažuriraj sve`, :guilabel:`Ažuriraj izabrane` "
"ili :guilabel:`Ažuriraj filtrirane` prema svojoj potrebi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:646
msgid "Quick Field Calculation Bar"
msgstr "Traka za brzo računanje polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:653
msgid "Editing multiple fields"
msgstr "Uređivanje više polja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:655
msgid ""
"Unlike the previous tools, multi edit mode allows multiple attributes of "
"different features to be edited simultaneously. When the layer is toggled to"
" edit, multi edit capabilities are accessible:"
msgstr ""
"Za razliku od prethodnih alatki, režim višestrukog uređivanja omogućava "
"istovremeno uređivanje više atributa različitih objekata. Kada se sloj "
"prebaci u uređivanje, mogućnosti višestrukog uređivanja su dostupne:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:659
msgid ""
"using the |multiEdit| :sup:`Toggle multi edit mode` button from the toolbar "
"inside the attribute table dialog;"
msgstr ""
"pomoću dugmeta |multiEdit| :sup:`Uključi/isključi režim višestrukog "
"uređivanja` iz palete alatki unutar dijaloga atributske tabele;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:661
msgid ""
"or selecting :menuselection:`Edit -->` |multiEdit| :menuselection:`Modify "
"attributes of selected features` menu."
msgstr ""
"ili izborom menija :menuselection:`Uređivanje -->` |multiEdit| "
":menuselection:`Izmeni atribute izabranih objekata`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:666
msgid ""
"Unlike the tool from the attribute table, hitting the :menuselection:`Edit "
"--> Modify Attributes of Selected Features` option provides you with a modal"
" dialog to fill attributes changes. Hence, features selection is required "
"before execution."
msgstr ""
"Za razliku od alata iz atributske tabele, izbor opcije "
":menuselection:`Uređivanje --> Izmeni atribute izabranih objekata` pruža vam"
" modalni dijalog za popunjavanje izmena atributa. Zato je izbor objekata "
"potreban pre izvršavanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:671
msgid "In order to edit multiple fields in a row:"
msgstr "Da biste uredili više polja odjednom:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:673
msgid "Select the features you want to edit."
msgstr "Izaberite objekte koje želite da uredite."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:674
msgid ""
"From the attribute table toolbar, click the |multiEdit| button. This will "
"toggle the dialog to its form view. Feature selection could also be made at "
"this step."
msgstr ""
"Iz palete alatki atributske tabele kliknite na dugme |multiEdit|. Time će se"
" dijalog prebaciti u prikaz obrasca. Izbor objekata takođe se može napraviti"
" u ovom koraku."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:677
msgid ""
"At the right side of the attribute table, fields (and values) of selected "
"features are shown. New widgets appear next to each field allowing for "
"display of the current multi edit state:"
msgstr ""
"Sa desne strane atributske tabele prikazana su polja (i vrednosti) izabranih"
" objekata. Novi vidžeti se pojavljuju pored svakog polja omogućavajući "
"prikaz trenutnog stanja višestrukog uređivanja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:681
msgid ""
"|multiEditMixedValues| The field contains different values for selected "
"features. It's shown empty and each feature will keep its original value. "
"You can reset the value of the field from the drop-down list of the widget."
msgstr ""
"|multiEditMixedValues| Polje sadrži različite vrednosti za izabrane objekte."
" Prikazano je prazno i svaki objekat će zadržati svoju originalnu vrednost. "
"Vrednost polja možete resetovati iz padajuće liste vidžeta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:857
msgid "multiEditMixedValues"
msgstr "multiEditMixedValues"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:684
msgid ""
"|multiEditSameValues| All selected features have the same value for this "
"field and the value displayed in the form will be kept."
msgstr ""
"|multiEditSameValues| Svi izabrani objekti imaju istu vrednost za ovo polje "
"i vrednost prikazana u obrascu će biti zadržana."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:859
msgid "multiEditSameValues"
msgstr "multiEditSameValues"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:686
msgid ""
"|multiEditChangedValues| The field has been edited and the entered value "
"will be applied to all the selected features. A message appears at the top "
"of the dialog, inviting you to either apply or reset your modification."
msgstr ""
"|multiEditChangedValues| Polje je uređeno i unesena vrednost će biti "
"primenjena na sve izabrane objekte. Poruka se pojavljuje na vrhu dijaloga, "
"pozivajući vas da primenite ili resetujete svoju izmenu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:855
msgid "multiEditChangedValues"
msgstr "multiEditChangedValues"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:690
msgid ""
"Clicking any of these widgets allows you to either set the current value for"
" the field or reset to original value, meaning that you can roll back "
"changes on a field-by-field basis."
msgstr ""
"Klik na bilo koji od ovih vidžeta omogućava vam da ili postavite trenutnu "
"vrednost za polje ili resetujete na originalnu vrednost, što znači da možete"
" poništiti izmene polje po polje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:699
msgid "Editing fields of multiple features"
msgstr "Uređivanje polja više objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:701
msgid "Make the changes to the fields you want."
msgstr "Napravite izmene na poljima koja želite."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:702
msgid ""
"Click on **Apply changes** in the upper message text or any other feature in"
" the left panel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na **Primeni izmene** u gornjem tekstu poruke ili na bilo koji "
"drugi objekat u levom panelu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:705
msgid ""
"Changes will apply to **all selected features**. If no feature is selected, "
"the whole table is updated with your changes. Modifications are made as a "
"single edit command. So pressing |undo| :sup:`Undo` will rollback the "
"attribute changes for all selected features at once."
msgstr ""
"Izmene će se primeniti na **sve izabrane objekte**. Ako nijedan objekat nije"
" izabran, cela tabela se ažurira vašim izmenama. Izmene se vrše kao jedna "
"komanda uređivanja. Zato će pritiskanje |undo| :sup:`Opozovi` poništiti "
"izmene atributa za sve izabrane objekte odjednom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:897
msgid "undo"
msgstr "undo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:712
msgid ""
"Multi edit mode is only available for auto generated and drag and drop forms"
" (see :ref:`customize_form`); it is not supported by custom ui forms."
msgstr ""
"Režim višestrukog uređivanja dostupan je samo za automatski generisane "
"obrasce i obrasce prevlačenja (pogledajte :ref:`customize_form`); ne "
"podržavaju ga prilagođeni ui obrasci."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:719
msgid "Exploring features attributes through the Identify Tool"
msgstr "Istraživanje atributa objekata pomoću alatke Identifikuj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:721
msgid ""
"The |identify| :ref:`Identify features <identify>` tool can be used to "
"display all attributes of a feature in the map canvas. It is a quick way to "
"view and verify all data without having to search for it in the attribute "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Alatka |identify| :ref:`Identifikuj objekte <identify>` može se koristiti za"
" prikaz svih atributa objekta na platnu karte. To je brz način da se svi "
"podaci pregledaju i provere bez potrebe za njihovim traženjem u atributskoj "
"tabeli."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:849
msgid "identify"
msgstr "identify"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:725
msgid ""
"To use the :guilabel:`Identify features` tool for vector layers, follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Da biste koristili alatku :guilabel:`Identifikuj objekte` za vektorske "
"slojeve, pratite ove korake:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:727
msgid "Select the vector layer in the Layers panel."
msgstr "Izaberite vektorski sloj u panelu Slojevi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:728
msgid ""
"Click on the :guilabel:`Identify features` tool in the toolbar or press "
":kbd:`Ctrl+Shift+I`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na alatku :guilabel:`Identifikuj objekte` u paleti alatki ili "
"pritisnite :kbd:`Ctrl+Shift+I`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:729
msgid "Click on a feature in the map view."
msgstr "Kliknite na objekat u prikazu karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:736
msgid "Identify Results dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog Rezultati identifikacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:738
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Identify results` panel will display different features "
"information in a tree view. There are two columns in the panel: "
":guilabel:`Feature` and :guilabel:`Value`. The first item is the name of the"
" layer and its children are its identified feature(s). Each feature is "
"identified by the :ref:`display name <maptips>` field along with its value. "
"Other information about the feature follows:"
msgstr ""
"Panel :guilabel:`Rezultati identifikacije` prikazaće različite informacije o"
" objektima u prikazu stabla. U panelu postoje dve kolone: "
":guilabel:`Objekat` i :guilabel:`Vrednost`. Prva stavka je naziv sloja, a "
"njena deca su njegov(i) identifikovan(i) objekat(i). Svaki objekat se "
"identifikuje poljem :ref:`prikazanog naziva <maptips>` zajedno sa njegovom "
"vrednošću. Slede druge informacije o objektu:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:745
msgid ""
"**Derived** section - those are the information calculated or derived from "
"other information in the layer. For example, the area of a polygon or the "
"length of a line. General information that can be found in this section:"
msgstr ""
"Odeljak **Izvedeno** - to su informacije izračunate ili izvedene iz drugih "
"informacija u sloju. Na primer, površina poligona ili dužina linije. Opšte "
"informacije koje se mogu naći u ovom odeljku:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:749
msgid ""
"Depending on the geometry type, the cartesian measurements of length, "
"perimeter or area in the layer's CRS units. For 3D line vectors, the "
"cartesian line length is available."
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od tipa geometrije, kartezijanska merenja dužine, obima ili "
"površine u jedinicama CRS-a sloja. Za 3D linijske vektore, dostupna je "
"kartezijanska dužina linije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:752
msgid ""
"Depending on the geometry type and if an ellipsoid is set in the "
":guilabel:`Project Properties` dialog (:menuselection:`General --> "
"Measurements`), ellipsoidal values of length, perimeter, or area using the "
"specified units."
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od tipa geometrije i ako je elipsoid postavljen u dijalogu "
":guilabel:`Svojstva projekta` (:menuselection:`Opšte --> Merenja`), "
"elipsoidne vrednosti dužine, obima ili površine pomoću zadatih jedinica."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:755
msgid ""
"The count of geometry parts in the feature and the number of the part "
"clicked."
msgstr "Broj delova geometrije u objektu i broj dela na koji je kliknuto."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:756
msgid "The count of vertices in the feature."
msgstr "Broj temena u objektu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:758
msgid ""
"Coordinate information, using the project properties :guilabel:`Coordinates "
"display` settings:"
msgstr ""
"Informacije o koordinatama, pomoću podešavanja :guilabel:`Prikaz koordinata`"
" u svojstvima projekta:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:761
msgid "``X`` and ``Y`` coordinate values of the clicked point"
msgstr "``X`` i ``Y`` vrednosti koordinata tačke na koju je kliknuto"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:762
msgid "the number of the closest vertex to the clicked point"
msgstr "broj najbližeg temena tački na koju je kliknuto"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:763
msgid ""
"``X`` and ``Y`` coordinate values of the closest vertex (and ``Z``/``M`` if "
"applicable)"
msgstr ""
"``X`` i ``Y`` vrednosti koordinata najbližeg temena (i ``Z``/``M`` ako je "
"primenljivo)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:765
msgid ""
"if you click on a curved segment, the radius of that section is also "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"ako kliknete na zakrivljeni segment, prikazuje se i poluprečnik tog dela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:766
msgid ""
"if both the vector layer and the project have vertical datums set and they "
"differ, the ``Z`` value will be displayed for both datums."
msgstr ""
"ako i vektorski sloj i projekat imaju postavljene vertikalne datume i oni se"
" razlikuju, ``Z`` vrednost će biti prikazana za oba datuma."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:769
msgid ""
"**Actions**: Actions can be added to the identify feature windows. The "
"action is run by clicking on the action label. By default, only one action "
"is added, namely ``View feature form`` for editing. You can define more "
"actions in the layer's properties dialog (see :ref:`actions_menu`)."
msgstr ""
"**Radnje**: Radnje se mogu dodati u prozore identifikacije objekta. Radnja "
"se pokreće klikom na natpis radnje. Podrazumevano se dodaje samo jedna "
"radnja, tj. ``Prikaži obrazac objekta`` za uređivanje. Više radnji možete "
"definisati u dijalogu svojstava sloja (pogledajte :ref:`actions_menu`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:773
msgid ""
"**Data attributes**: This is the list of attribute fields and values for the"
" feature that has been clicked."
msgstr ""
"**Atributi podataka**: Ovo je lista atributskih polja i vrednosti za objekat"
" na koji je kliknuto."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:776
msgid ""
"Links in the feature's attributes are clickable from the :guilabel:`Identify"
" Results` panel and will open in your default web browser."
msgstr ""
"Linkovi u atributima objekta mogu se kliknuti iz panela :guilabel:`Rezultati"
" identifikacije` i otvoriće se u vašem podrazumevanom veb pregledaču."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:780
msgid ""
"When a vector layer has defined :ref:`relations <vector_relations>`, the "
":guilabel:`Identify Results` panel can display both **referenced** and "
"**referencing** related features. To view these relations, ensure that the "
":guilabel:`Show relations` option is enabled in the :ref:`Identify Settings "
"<identify_toolbar>`. Available information for each related feature include:"
msgstr ""
"Kada vektorski sloj ima definisane :ref:`relacije <vector_relations>`, panel"
" :guilabel:`Rezultati identifikacije` može prikazati i **referencirane** i "
"**referencirajuće** povezane objekte. Da biste videli ove relacije, uverite "
"se da je opcija :guilabel:`Prikaži relacije` omogućena u :ref:`Podešavanjima"
" identifikacije <identify_toolbar>`. Dostupne informacije za svaki povezani "
"objekat uključuju:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:787
msgid "the name of the relation and the linked layer"
msgstr "naziv relacije i povezani sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:788
msgid ""
"the entry in the referenced or referencing field, identifying the feature"
msgstr ""
"unos u referenciranom ili referencirajućem polju, koji identifikuje objekat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:789
msgid "the activated actions"
msgstr "aktivirane radnje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:790
msgid "the list of attribute fields and values"
msgstr "listu atributskih polja i vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:792
msgid ""
"You can expand related features to explore connected records through "
"multiple levels, including many-to-many (n:m) and polymorphic relations. "
"Only nodes you explicitly expand are loaded, preventing excessive nesting."
msgstr ""
"Povezane objekte možete proširiti da biste istražili povezane zapise kroz "
"više nivoa, uključujući relacije više-prema-više (n:m) i polimorfne "
"relacije. Učitavaju se samo čvorovi koje eksplicitno proširite, sprečavajući"
" preterano ugnežđivanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/attribute_table.rst:796
msgid ""
"To focus on a specific related record, right-click it and choose "
":guilabel:`Identify Feature`. This re-centers the identify results on the "
"selected feature, starting a new identification tree from it and effectively"
" limiting the visible nesting depth. Features already shown in ancestor "
"nodes are automatically omitted to avoid duplicates or circular relations."
msgstr ""
"Da biste se fokusirali na određeni povezani zapis, kliknite desnim tasterom "
"na njega i izaberite :guilabel:`Identifikuj objekat`. Time se rezultati "
"identifikacije ponovo centriraju na izabrani objekat, počinjući novo stablo "
"identifikacije od njega i efektivno ograničavajući vidljivu dubinu "
"ugnežđivanja. Objekti već prikazani u nadređenim čvorovima automatski se "
"izostavljaju radi izbegavanja duplikata ili kružnih relacija."
